$ MS Office Add-In

Add-Ins are components that can be installed on the computer to augment the functionality of Office products.

→ Microsoft/Office[MS Office] add-ins include the following technologies:
  • → Windows/development/COM add-ins
  • Visual Studio for Office (VSTO) add-ins
  • Automation add-ins
  • RealTimeData (RTD) servers
  • Application add-ins (such as `.wll`, → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Add-ins/XLL[`.xll`,] `.xlam`, …)
  • → development/XML expansion packs
  • XML style sheets
  

The extent of trust granted to add-ins can be controlled in the → Microsoft/Office/security/Trust-Center.

