sa:

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Add-ins[Add-Ins (Excel)]

  The menu → Microsoft/Office/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/File/Options/Add-ins[File -> Options -> Add-ins] allows to enable or disable add-ins.

  Which Add-Ins are loaded for a specific Office product is stored in the → Windows/registry under the key
  → Windows/registry/tree/HK_CU-LM/Software/Microsoft/Office/application_name/Addins[`HKLM|HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Office\{application-name}\Addins`]

  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Office/root/OfficeN/Library[`C:\Program Files\Microsoft Office\root\OfficeX\Library`]

  The → Microsoft/Office/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Developer[Developer tab on the Ribbon]
